{"tid":891292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4歲女童醫院ICU內被5男輪姦","createTime":"2018-11-06T04:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T05:44:32.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bba489b443e52e5eab4515e7c500bf846f97e0","tid":891292,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"印度北方邦首府勒克瑙一間醫院發生風化案，一名在深切治療部留醫的4歲女童報稱遭5名男子輪姦。警方現已拘捕一名涉案男子，正繼續追緝其他疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n案中女童因被蛇咬，已於醫院留醫4日。案發在上周六（3日）晚上，深切治療部只有女童一人，其間被一名醫院男工聯同4名男子性侵。事後這名女童告知祖母，揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方已調查閉路電視片段，並拘捕其中一名疑犯，惟未有透露這名疑犯資料。<br />\n（獨立報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181105/s00005/1541376033916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181105%2Fs00005%2F1541376033916&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZptr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a4bd3a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181105%2Fs00005%2F1541376033916&h=c09ee106\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181105/s00005/1541376033916</a>"},{"pid":"35fd3570bd62e8695a4b746ca6e39c0195685f5d","tid":891292,"uid":57217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，細路女都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f8804c92bb83359bfa7f6a23b760e6ab703997","tid":891292,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線 分分鐘插撚住喉都照屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bde1096431456791156a5f6d801421af8a3c56","tid":891292,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"屌成班仆街<br />\n攞哂去閹啦"},{"pid":"e7ceb26841c1046e1e593acf535bd7cbae456b9e","tid":891292,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T